<title>USA: Crystal Systems IPO to price tonight - underwriter.</title>
<headline>Crystal Systems IPO to price tonight - underwriter.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Crystal Systems Solution Ltd will come to market earlier than previously expected, lead underwriter Hampshire Securities said Thursday.</p>
<p>The company's initial public offering of three million shares is now due to price later today, the underwriter said. It had been scheduled for next week.  </p>
<p>The company makes software designed to address the &quot;Year 2000 problem,&quot; which is a glitch that could cause many computers to crash when the date rolls over from 1999 to 2000.</p>
<p>It plans to offer three million shares, Hampshire said.</p>
